==Arabic==
===Etymology===
From the root verb {{ARchar|[[شهد]]}} (šáhida), to [[witness]], to bear witness.

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|شهيد}}''' (šahīd) {{m}}, {{ARchar|[[شهداء]]}} (šuhadā’) {{p}}

# [[witness]].
# [[martyr]], someone killed in battle with the [[infidel]]s.
# anyone killed in action.

